Constructor
-----------
1. Constructor is a special member function. 
2. Name of Constructor is same as class name.
3. Constructor does not return any value not even void.
4. Constructor will be called automatically, when ever object of a class is created.
5. Initial work of Constructor is to construct class.
6. Constructor is responsible for providing default initial values to data members.
7. Types of Constructor : 
    a. Default constructor | No argument constructor
    b. Parameterized constructor 
    c. Copy constructor (default copy constructor is absent)